OL,5, A paedophile who pleaded guilty to     
OL,6, sexually abusing two girls has been    
OL,7, allowed to jet off on holiday to Greece
OL,8, before being sentenced.                
OL,10,FMatthew Thompson, 48, is set to fly to 
OL,11,FKos for a week-long break despite      
OL,12,Ffacing a possible jail term.           
OL,14,FThompson, from Barnsley, admitted 10   
OL,15,Foffences, including sexual assault and 
OL,16,Ftaking indecent images of a child.     
OL,18,FJudge Jonathan Gibson said despite his 
OL,19,Fpleas he would not revoke bail ahead of
OL,20,Fsentencing on 18 November.             
